本仓库 (Elaina Engine · 伊蕾娜引擎) 内容仅供学习与技术研究使用。

This repository (Elaina Engine) is provided for educational and research
purposes only.

================================================================================
重要声明 / Important Notice
================================================================================

1. 来源 / Origin
   本仓库的核心代码来自对某商业游戏服务端 DLL 的反编译, 经过反混淆、重命名、
   结构重组、安全加固等多轮加工. 仓库维护者对该商业代码的原始版权不主张所有权.

   The core code in this repository originated from decompilation of a
   commercial game server DLL, subsequently deobfuscated, renamed, reorganized
   and hardened against multiple security vulnerabilities. The repository
   maintainer makes NO claim of ownership over the original commercial code.

2. 允许的用途 / Permitted Use
   - 个人学习 .NET / C# / 游戏服务端架构 / 网络协议 / 安全审计
   - 学术研究, 包括但不限于公开发表的安全分析、架构论文等
   - 引用本仓库内容时, 请保留本声明并注明来源链接

   - Personal study of .NET / C# / game server architecture / network
     protocols / security auditing
   - Academic research, including but not limited to publicly disclosed
     security analyses and architecture papers
   - When quoting content from this repository, please preserve this notice
     and include a link back to the source

3. 禁止的用途 / Prohibited Use
   - 直接运营商业游戏服务器或以盈利为目的部署本代码
   - 重新分发时移除本声明、SECURITY_AUDIT.md 或 CHANGELOG.md
   - 任何违反所在司法管辖区相关法律的使用方式

   - Operating commercial game servers for profit using this code
   - Redistribution that removes this LICENSE, SECURITY_AUDIT.md, or
     CHANGELOG.md
   - Any use that violates the laws of your jurisdiction

